attributes.title: it caused a tornado!!!!
attributes.review: i originally downloaded this application to support the fellow squirrels in the neighborhood as i had thought that our president- donald jenius trump- had fully supported them throughout his four years in office🧚✨😻 and you can imagine my surprise when as soon as i had launched the app it glitched and showed me a very disturbing message saying that the person reading this was ugly 🙀😪✨ i was shocked!!! i then filled up my shopping cart with many items supporting our jenius president 2020 when i totally forgot to checkout! anyway once i closed the app i proceeded about my day when i heard a shattering of glass and i saw that my windows had all shattered ☹️🙀🤪 i was so very confused and then i saw a group of squirrels of all people grouping outside my house! ☎️🌚🐩 i deducted that the only reasonable explanation for this was this very app i had downloaded in hopes of supporting the very group that was gathered outside my house protesting again donald jenius!🦩👨‍👨‍👦🦹 and just as i was sure everything was alright again a giant tornado appeared out of nowhere!!!! imagine that! this app had caused a giant tornado 🌪☄️🦆 my golly gosh! the tornado sucked me and my house up and brought us to the land of oz 🙀😰🧚✨🏡 the wizard of oz told me to get home i had to delete this wretched app so i did as he said i all was normal again.🤩😝✌️🥰😚🤩 so i learned, mr donald jenius trump, some people do great things with their lives😍🧚✨you are not one of them😚✨🧚
